14:19.000 --> 14:26.000
with a sum no less than the tax on profit, then it is exempted from paying this tax.

14:27.000 --> 14:28.000
Pay attention.

14:29.000 --> 14:36.000
In this case, any businessman is interested in showing the maximum profit.

14:37.000 --> 14:40.000
And this profit is invested in the development of his own business.

14:41.000 --> 14:47.000
And no one hides, even a penny, a penny, no one will hide the profit from tax deductions.

14:48.000 --> 14:54.000
