15:40.000 --> 15:42.000
And does not strive to get the maximum profit.

15:42.000 --> 15:43.000
This is the worst.

15:44.000 --> 15:48.000
One thing is when a business does not strive to show its profit, but strives to create it.

15:49.000 --> 15:52.000
