32:49.000 --> 32:53.000
that it does not completely refuse it and is thinking about its receipt.

32:54.000 --> 32:59.000
And we, as financiers, who are designed to provide financial registration

32:59.000 --> 33:03.000
and the proper execution of the profit,

33:04.000 --> 33:09.000
must make sure that the enterprise receives as much profit as possible.

33:10.000 --> 33:12.000
In addition to the accounting policy,

33:13.000 --> 33:17.000
