33:18.000 --> 33:23.000
First of all, the volume of goods and services produced.

33:23.000 --> 33:26.000
It is clear that the more goods and services are produced,

33:27.000 --> 33:31.000
the more opportunities are available to make a profit.

33:32.000 --> 33:36.000
In addition to the total volume, the structure of the produced product also affects.

33:37.000 --> 33:43.000
In fact, among the produced products there are more or less quality,

33:44.000 --> 33:46.000
more expensive or less expensive,

33:47.000 --> 33:49.000
which bring more profit or less profit,

33:50.000 --> 33:52.000
which are more profitable or less profitable,

33:53.000 --> 33:58.000
and the structure of the enterprise can increase the total amount of profit.

33:59.000 --> 34:02.000
The price level is not the last place.

34:03.000 --> 34:06.000
By regulating the prices of their products,

34:07.000 --> 34:11.000
in the aspect in which the enterprise can do it on its own,

34:12.000 --> 34:14.000
you can achieve an increase in profit.

34:15.000 --> 34:20.000
And, of course, the most important point is self-worth.

34:20.000 --> 34:25.000
