45:10.000 --> 45:11.000
As a result, even the most unelastic product, salt,

45:12.000 --> 45:14.000
is sold at a very low price.

45:15.000 --> 45:17.000
But if the manufacturers enter into a contract

45:18.000 --> 45:20.000
and agree that they will sell,

45:21.000 --> 45:23.000
for example, at the same price,

45:24.000 --> 45:26.000
all salt manufacturers,

