45:34.000 --> 45:36.000
the price of salt will go higher and higher.

45:37.000 --> 45:38.000
There is no competition.

45:39.000 --> 45:40.000
Salt is the most unelastic product,

45:41.000 --> 45:42.000
and the price increase

45:43.000 --> 45:44.000
